owltools.reasoner

Class LazyExpressionMaterializingReasoner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.semanticweb.owlapi.reasoner.impl.OWLReasonerBase
      • owltools.reasoner.LazyExpressionMaterializingReasoner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.semanticweb.owlapi.reasoner.OWLReasoner
    Deprecated. 
    This is no longer necessary as ELK 0.4 supports queries using class expressions.

    @Deprecated
public class LazyExpressionMaterializingReasoner
extends org.semanticweb.owlapi.reasoner.impl.OWLReasonerBase
implements org.semanticweb.owlapi.reasoner.OWLReasoner
    Wraps a reasoner. Any queries involving class expressions are first materialized to classes. Primarily for use with Elk (0.3)
    Author:
    cjm
